							<div id="page-title"><div class="header-side-left"></div>
								<h2>Open Publishing Guide</h2>
								<div class="header-side-right"></div></div>
			
                                        
          <div class="view view-frontpage view-id-frontpage view-display-id-page view-dom-id-1">
        <div class="view-header">
      <div id="frontpage-mainheader">
<div id="frontpage_mainText">
<p class="header-text">
The Open Publishing Guide has everything you need to know to publish your work. 
</p>
<p class="header-text">
Watch your idea become a reality. From a concept to a tangible item, we guide you through the publishing process.
</p>
</div>
